# Athlete Pro — Antigravity Protocol

## Project Context
- [cite_start]Stack: Vanilla JS, IndexedDB, Node.js, Supabase. [cite: 4, 5]
- [cite_start]Design: Vantablack Luxury (#0a0a0f). [cite: 6]

## Architecture Rules
- [cite_start]Store/View Pattern: Logic in `.store.js`, DOM in `.view.js`. [cite: 6]
- Sync: Outbox pattern with exponential backoff (SyncStore).
- Idempotency: Always UPSERT to Supabase by record ID.

## iOS Safari & PWA
- No Background Sync: Use `visibilitychange` + `online` triggers.
- Persistent Storage: Call `navigator.storage.persist()` on app start.
- [cite_start]Haptics: Use `navigator.vibrate?.([15, 50, 15])` for feedback. [cite: 7]

## Testing Standards
- 100% pass rate required for Offline Flow (Block 3) and Data Integrity (Block 8).